Dialogue: 9,0:00:00.93,0:00:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see that thing on TV yesterday?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:02.91,0:00:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See what?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:03.91,0:00:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 9,0:00:05.26,0:00:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Reporters on the scene! The truth behind Hamanoko's giant eel, Hussy!"
Dialogue: 9,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that too!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:11.49,0:00:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it actually exists.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:14.10,0:00:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The ghost, when examined, was just withered flowers." Right, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a boring guy.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you feel any sort of romance?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:23.14,0:00:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious about whether it exists or not.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:26.10,0:00:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't care if it does or not, but I hope it does.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:30.06,0:00:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it more interesting that way?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:31.88,0:00:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All ghosts are just withered flowers.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:35.13,0:00:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so you.
