Dialogue: 9,0:02:11.80,0:02:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are the four of us being shaken around on this bus?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:14.89,0:02:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer to that, of course, lies in this bus's destination.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its final stop, Zaizen Village, is famous for mountain hiking and hot springs.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going for the hot springs, not the hiking.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:25.76,0:02:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally I'd much rather be taking a break from everything during my summer "break", however...
Dialogue: 9,0:02:30.68,0:02:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for helping me with my uncle, Oreki-san.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:34.50,0:02:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all take a trip to the hot springs together?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the hot springs!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... Let's go...
Dialogue: 9,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be coming by to pick us up any time now.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really great view.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Oreki-san?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:52.66,0:02:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:53.86,0:02:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's typical Houtarou for you. Already complaining.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only one and a half hours.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:59.13,0:03:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, good job getting us these rooms, Mayaka.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:02.66,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My relatives are in the middle of renovating their inn and can't take guests, so they're letting us stay for free.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, Oreki-san.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! We're here!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki, hurry up or we're leaving you there.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! Our inn!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:24.26,0:03:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Seizansou.
