Dialogue: 9,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the elder sister, Zenna Rie,
Dialogue: 9,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is her younger sister, Zenna Kayo.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in fourth and sixth grades.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:36.69,0:03:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure grown—
Dialogue: 9,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your rooms are the last two on the second floor.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:43.46,0:03:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Houtarou! Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:48.68,0:03:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room has a great view!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this kind of thing isn't bad every now and then.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:54.51,0:03:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I think it would have been more dignified to come alone.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, traveling alone?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:03.04,0:04:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:04.14,0:04:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that you're here because Chitanda planned it and Mayaka had connections.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food's ready!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for dinner!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:22.57,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that cheese?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stew.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gratin.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese fondue.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chilled shabushabu?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's dessert too.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:35.78,0:04:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it cheesecake?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:37.98,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could smell it.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:41.86,0:04:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just like Maya-neechan said!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you tell them, Ibara?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:46.81,0:04:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play with fireworks tomorrow!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:49.66,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Dad bought some yesterday and—
Dialogue: 9,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:54.74,0:04:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:55.92,0:04:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you burn yourself?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:59.69,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more careful next time.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was good...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:08.02,0:05:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Satoshi already head to the bath?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:19.40,0:05:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess this is a hot springs inn, after all...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you headed to?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same place you are.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ibara?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:31.21,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids took her somewhere.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:34.35,0:05:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be a bit random, but what kind of person is your sister?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:38.93,0:05:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That seriously is random...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, you're an only child, aren't you?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:44.60,0:05:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister, huh?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:45.85,0:05:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could call her an oddball, and you could call her a genius.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:49.88,0:05:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that I could be better than her at anything.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:53.62,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I've never really cared to be.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why my sister all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of the Zenna sisters?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:05.08,0:06:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I've always wanted a sibling.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:08.83,0:06:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An older sister or a younger brother...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:09.95,0:06:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's wonderful to have someone you can go to for anything always there for you?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this young lady is far too optimistic.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks her dreams are true for everyone.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having siblings in reality isn't wonderful in the slightest.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this isn't a mixed bath...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Grandpa!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:53.67,0:06:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bigger than I thought...
Dialogue: 9,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Houtarou!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bath is great!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's practically flowing through my body!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:20.49,0:07:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting your blood diluted with water is dangerous.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:24.16,0:07:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you think of something more interesting to say?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:26.83,0:07:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it shows you're relaxing.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:36.51,0:07:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Chitanda?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki?!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bath made him dizzy.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of pathetic, really.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:11.61,0:08:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hadn't even been in there half as long as me, but when I turned around, he'd almost passed out.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a...
Dialogue: 9,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:31.29,0:08:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki...
Dialogue: 9,0:08:32.20,0:08:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fated never to enjoy an event.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:37.68,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm still sick from that bus ride.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel awful.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:58.04,0:09:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki-san? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:03.62,0:09:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still hot...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I get a cold towel for you?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:08.35,0:09:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to sleep.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:13.26,0:09:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you worry when we're out on a trip like this...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:18.65,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, we're going to tell ghost stories in a bit.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:22.71,0:09:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling better, you're welcome to join us.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you feel better soon.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:29.05,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even eight yet...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drums?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:47.05,0:09:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we don't really need the annex.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the window next door is open, too...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:55.73,0:09:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This inn has a secret.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:58.47,0:10:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, a gloomy customer came to stay.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:01.67,0:10:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was put in room seven in the main building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:04.54,Open,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(110,0)\blur1\fs50\c&H002332&\frz6.328\pos(607.857,301.286)}7
Dialogue: 9,0:10:04.54,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told them, "I don't need meals or room service. Just stay away."
Dialogue: 9,0:10:09.83,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he'd already paid in advance, and it was the busy season, so he was a perfect guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:14.42,Open,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay-0.3\fad(0,0)\blur1\fs50\c&H002332&\frz6.328\frx356\fry338\pos(950.257,285.286)}7
Dialogue: 9,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that evening, a piercing scream echoed throughout the inn.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:19.16,0:10:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scream?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:20.64,0:10:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guest in room seven had hanged himself, and his body was swaying in the wind.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:27.06,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he had embezzled money from his company and run away.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:33.27,0:10:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that incident, guests staying in room seven all say the same thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:38.70,Open,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,460)\blur1\fs35\c&H102F38&\frz12.13\move(934.533,516.533,962.533,515.199,27,1320)}2
Dialogue: 9,0:10:37.82,0:10:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There's something in this room. I see shadows at night."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.20,Open,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,460)\blur1\fs35\c&H123245&\frz12.13\move(820,266,848,264,27,1320)}3
