Dialogue: 9,0:10:43.16,0:10:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the ninth guest in that room...
Dialogue: 9,0:10:46.59,0:10:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:48.33,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the night, he suddenly succumbed to an unknown illness!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:51.88,0:10:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:52.80,0:10:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop it!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:55.34,0:11:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Grandma asked for an exorcism and had the annex built.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:00.52,0:11:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to stop any bad rumors from spreading.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this room seven?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it right across from this window.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That room there.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:09.61,0:11:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We live on the first floor, and we're told to stay away from the second floor.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. You're joking.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:16.76,0:11:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone I told you, okay?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:19.44,0:11:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that one before.
